race.comment: WHATJEUDOIN' (12) has hit a patch of form with a win and four seconds from his past five starts. Down in the weights and shouldn't be discounted lightly. DEMARCAY (9) is a consistent conveyance who has hit the top-five in 11 of his past 12 starts. Rock-hard fit and is a must for the exotics players. TECHNA (11) hasn't been too far away in recent outings and may earn some minor money from the favourable draw. LIBERTY PARK (7) has been in the market at his last couple of starts but hasn't made an impression, last start running sixth at this track. Damien Thornton goes on and look for an improved run.
